Description: eSim - Open Source EDA Tool by FOSSEE, IIT Bombay
 eSim is an integrated open-source Electronic Design Automation (EDA) tool
 for circuit design, simulation, and PCB design. It is built on top of KiCad
 and integrates Ngspice and NGHDL for mixed-signal and digital simulation.
 .
 Developed by the FOSSEE group at IIT Bombay.
